The evidence with the title 'Is $250,000 middle class? Hillary Clinton and Bernie Sanders think ... ' says Feb 18, 2016  ... Your price tag for the Obama economy  ... For Hillary Clinton and Bernie Sanders , the middle class extends to those earning up to $ 250,000 a year. Both have used that figure as the dividing line , raising taxes on those with higher incomes as part of their campaigns to ensure the wealthy pay their fair share . 
